g\nthe way to large scale integrations. Our techniques can be used to improve\nscaling of quantum networks relying on diamond spins, phosphorous in silicon or\nother spin systems like quantum dots, silicon carbide or rare earth ions in\nsolids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2013 08:30:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2013 07:52:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-20"}
